.Dd October 30, 2014
.Dt MOPHERCTL 8
.Os @PACKAGE_STRING@
.Sh NAME
.Nm mopherctl
.Nd the mopher daemon control utility
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl h
.Op Fl d Ar level
.Op Fl c Ar file
.Op Fl s Ar host
.Ar command
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
controls the mopher daemon.
.Pp
Available options are:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl h
Show usage message.
.It Fl d Ar level
Set logging severity level to
.Ar level
.It Fl c Ar file
Read configuration from
.Ar file .
.It Fl s Ar host
Connect to
.Ar host .
.El
.Pp
.Ar command
is one of the following:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It dump Ar table
Print raw content of
.Ar table .
.It greylist dump
Print formatted content of the greylist-table.
.It greylist pass Ar origin Ar from Ar rcpt
Temporarily whitelist triplet.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Pa @CONFIG_PATH@/mopherd.conf
Configuration file for the mopher daemon.
.It Pa @CONFIG_PATH@/mopherd.acl
List of rules enforced by the mopher daemon.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr mopher 7 ,
.Xr mopherd.conf 5 ,
.Xr mopherd.acl 5
